_sText:
hg_warehouse is a HungerGames map for Counter-Strike: Source

All my maps previously have been made just for the ]HeLL[ Clan but I've decided to upload them to GameBanana.

More maps to come, comment or PM me about bugs or improvements to my maps so I can edit and update them.

I hope you enjoy!

Features:
- 32 spawns
- 13 rooms
- Made to suit a low populated HungerGames server
- Detailed Crate System:

- Knife
- Glock
- USP
- Elites
- Fiveseven
- Deagle
